docs.lead_paragraph: Mrs. Anna Olinger has no real explanation for her age of 103 years. "I suppose it's just that I've managed to change with the times," she told an interviewer not long ago.

headline.main: Slowing the clock of age; But what if people live to be 100 or more? Aging Picture Credits
